      <title>[후르츠 칵테일] (26화) 복숭아</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/weekend/2024/08/24/I3D3R6DVUVGQRGFB3KECTWVVBU/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/weekend/2024/08/24/I3D3R6DVUVGQRGFB3KECTWVVBU/</guid>
      <dc:creator>글·그림 조경규</dc:creator>
      <description/>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 15:40:00 +0000</pubDate>
